edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent

Class TrydentEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.gatech.cs2340.trydent.TrydentEngine

  • public class TrydentEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    Main class that kicks off the TrydentEngine. As a developer using the TrydentEngine, all you have to do is call TrydentEngine.start() to get started.
